 <purpose>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the description 
of a geometric shape by means of geometrically bounded wireframe models. 
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
  <li>points and curve geometry in 3D Cartesian space;</li>
  <li>use of wireframe geometry to represent a shape;</li>
  <li>combination of representations to form an aggregation of wireframe representations.</li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
